
# Building V8

First, enable RTTI and Exceptions in the GN build.

```
$ vi build/config/BUILDCONFIG.gn # Change no_rtti to rtti; Remove no_exceptions
$ python tools/dev/v8gen.py -vv x64.release -- is_component_build=true is_debug=false v8_enable_i18n_support=false v8_enable_inspector=false v8_deprecation_warnings=true
$ PATH=$PATH:~/code/depot_tools ninja -C out.gn/x64.release d8
```

Building `d8` will build the necessary *v8* libs required to build PyV8.

More info and GN options at https://github.com/v8/v8/wiki/Building%20with%20GN.

# Building PyV8

```
$ V8_HOME=../path-to-v8 python setup.py build
```

